OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations of misconduct
OL,6,FA Reform UK councillor has been
OL,7,Fsuspended after allegations of
OL,8,Fmisconduct from several women in an
OL,9,F"unofficial complaint".
OL,11,FRobert Ford, who represents Maidstone
OL,12,FRural West at Kent County Council
OL,13,F(KCC) after being elected as a Reform
OL,14,Fcouncillor in May, had the party whip
OL,15,Fremoved on Monday 13 October.
OL,17,FThe party says it will launch an
OL,18,Finternal investigation after multiple
OL,19,Ffemale members of staff at KCC made
OL,20,Fcomplaints about Mr Ford last week.
