OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations of misconduct
OL,6,FA statement from Reform UK said: "We
OL,7,Fhave today suspended the Reform UK
OL,8,Fwhip from councillor Robert Ford
OL,9,Fpending investigation into his conduct.
OL,11,F"Last week an unofficial complaint was
OL,12,Fmade against councillor Ford by
OL,13,Fseveral female members of staff.
OL,15,F"Despite being offered a meeting with
OL,16,Fthe whip's office to discuss the
OL,17,Fcomplaints, councillor Ford refused to
OL,18,Fengage with the process which has now
OL,19,Fescalated into a disciplinary matter."
