OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations of misconduct
OL,6,FMr Ford has suggested to the BBC that
OL,7,Fit "was a surprise" that any female
OL,8,Fmembers of staff had made a complaint.
OL,10,FMr Ford, who will now sit as an
OL,11,Findependent councillor, has been
OL,12,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,14,FEarlier this year, Reform UK suspended
OL,15,Fanother KCC councillor Daniel Taylor
OL,16,Ffollowing allegations that he had
OL,17,Fthreatened to kill his wife.
OL,19,FHe is set to stand trial at Margate
OL,20,FMagistrates Court in May next year.
